*xscreensaver-5.04 (30 Dec 2007)

  30 Dec 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  -files/xscreensaver-5.02-gdmflexiserver.patch,
  -files/xscreensaver-5.02-nsfw.patch, -files/xscreensaver-5.02-pam.patch,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.04-desktop-entry.patch,
  +files/xscreensaver-5.04-nsfw.patch, -xscreensaver-5.02-r2.ebuild,
  +xscreensaver-5.04.ebuild:
  Version bump. Use global use flag for setuid screensavers. Use up to date
  .desktop file from tarball patched to f.d.o desktop entry standard. Pass
  --with-x-app-defaults to econf instead of moving files around in D. Remove
  old version.

