*xscreensaver-4.22-r1 (24 Jun 2005)

  24 Jun 2005; Jonathan Smith <smithj@gentoo.org>
  +xscreensaver-4.22-r1.ebuild:
  removed yelp dependency; norpm patch merged with new configure patch; fixed
  gnome-terminal problem for #94708; fixed default local setting problem for
  #96914; changed hackdir to something more suitable; used new X11 library
